SUMMARY: Chase Rabideau @ Perihelion Brewery 
DTSTAMP:20260325T062316Z
DTSTART:20260325T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:A professional guitarist and singer of many musical backgrounds
	\, Chase Rabideau is a crowd-centered entertainer with a background in man
	y popular genres. Along with folk/rock centric original music that can be 
	found online\, Chase plays over 400 covers in a variety of genres such as 
	rock ‘n roll (50’s\, 60’s\, 70’s\, +more)\, classic country\, folk\, R&B\,
	 jazz\, blues\, folk/pub songs from Ireland\, (seasonal) Christmas music\,
	 and crowd-favorite popular music.\n\nhttps://www.perihelion.beer/events/2
	026/2/24/chase-rabideau-perihelion-brewery-mpbj4
URL:https://www.perihelion.beer/events/2026/2/24/chase-rabideau-perihelion-
	brewery-mpbj4
